description: Lists all schema extensions applied to a Microsoft AD Directory.

parameters.name: DirectoryId
parameters.description: The identifier of the directory from which to retrieve the schema extension information.

nested_items.name: SchemaExtensionsInfo
nested_items.description: Information about the schema extensions applied to the directory.

nested_items.name: DirectoryId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the directory to which the schema extension is applied.

nested_items.name: SchemaExtensionId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the schema extension.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: A description of the schema extension.

nested_items.name: SchemaExtensionStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the schema extension.

nested_items.name: StartDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the schema extension started being applied to the directory.

nested_items.name: EndDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the schema extension was completed.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If not null, more results are available. Pass this value for the NextToken parameter in a subsequent call to ListSchemaExtensions to retrieve the next set of items.
